
[1]juxtaposition

   JUXTAPOSI'TION, n. [L. juxta,near, and position.]

   A placing or being placed in nearness or contiguity; as the parts of a
   substance or of a composition. The connection of words is sometimes to
   be ascertained by juxtaposition.
